disponibilite\">Prix et disponibilit&eacute;</a></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 2.5px 0px 20px 12px; position: relative;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #2b2b2b; text-decoration-line: none; transition: color 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.25, 1); font-weight: bold;\" href=\"http://www.phonandroid.com/test-xiaomi-roborock-s50.html#conclusion\">Conclusion</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 7px; font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; color: #202120;\"><span id=\"video\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Vid&eacute;o</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"responsive-container embed-youtube-com\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; padding-bottom: 455.625px; height: 0px; overflow: hidden; max-width: 100%; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><iframe style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 24px; width: 810px; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; height: 455.625px;\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mKT8sTqiKqE?feature=oembed\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></div>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #3e3e3e; font-family: \'Open Sans\', sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 7px; font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif; color: #202120;\"><span id=\"fiche-technique\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Fiche technique</span></h2>\r\n<table id=\"tablepress-115\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-115\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0px; width: 810px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; border-top: non